{"nodes": [{"id": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp0_experiment_0_doc", "label": "Phase 1 Exp 0 \u2014 SCFF sanity gate card", "file_type": "document", "source_file": "draft6.0\\src\\phase1\\exp0\\experiment-0.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": null}, {"id": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp0_scff_gate", "label": "SCFF sanity gate (Exp 0)", "file_type": "concept", "source_file": "draft6.0\\src\\phase1\\exp0\\experiment-0.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "First thing run: does SCFF separate at all, and what is the full-GD ceiling? Gate PASSED (goodness separates, features class-separable, SCFF beats random on 64-D digits) with three forced config changes."}, {"id": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp0_sum_goodness", "label": "Sum-goodness G=\u2016h\u2016\u00b2", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "draft6.0\\src\\phase1\\exp0\\experiment-0.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "Sum not mean: with mean+unit-norm inputs deep-layer goodness is starved below \u03b8=2.0; sum-goodness is ~1.0 at init, width-independent, substrate-faithful (no per-weight Adam state) \u2014 vindicates ideas1's G=\u2016h\u2016\u00b2."}, {"id": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp0_checkerboard_task", "label": "2-D checkerboard gate task", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "draft6.0\\src\\phase1\\exp0\\experiment-0.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "16-cluster 4\u00d74 checkerboard chosen because it is density-separated AND too hard for random features \u2014 the spiral's equal-density interleaved arms defeat SCFF-alone (~0.55), so the spiral moved to the GD cells."}, {"id": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp0_scff_clusters_by_density", "label": "SCFF clusters by density, not class", "file_type": "rationale", "source_file": "draft6.0\\src\\phase1\\exp0\\experiment-0.md", "source_location": null, "source_url": null, "captured_at": null, "author": null, "contributor": null, "rationale": "SCFF's loss makes coherent samples loud and blends quiet, so it learns where the data is (density); this recovers classes only when classes are density-separated clusters. On low-D JL-easy data it does not beat a random projection; its learning only pays off in high-D."}], "edges": [{"source": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp0_experiment_0_doc", "target": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp0_scff_gate", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "draft6.0\\src\\phase1\\exp0\\experiment-0.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp0_experiment_0_doc", "target": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp0_sum_goodness", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "draft6.0\\src\\phase1\\exp0\\experiment-0.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp0_experiment_0_doc", "target": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp0_checkerboard_task", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "draft6.0\\src\\phase1\\exp0\\experiment-0.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp0_experiment_0_doc", "target": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp0_scff_clusters_by_density", "relation": "references", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "draft6.0\\src\\phase1\\exp0\\experiment-0.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}, {"source": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp0_scff_clusters_by_density", "target": "draft6_0_src_phase1_exp0_checkerboard_task", "relation": "rationale_for", "confidence": "EXTRACTED", "confidence_score": 1.0, "source_file": "draft6.0\\src\\phase1\\exp0\\experiment-0.md", "source_location": null, "weight": 1.0}], "hyperedges": []}